## If you need more context

If the above syntax reference is insufficient for a specific use case, you can:

1. **Read the full documentation** at: https://www.modcodepattern.com/docs
2. **Study real-world pattern examples** at: https://github.com/modcodepattern-saas/patterns-exemple
   — Navigate every subdirectory and read every `.json` file to understand advanced techniques
   such as `contentFilter`, glob exclusions like `**/!(*.spec|*.stories).tsx`,
   conditional bash commands, and Premium Git variables.

> Only reach for external resources if the built-in reference above doesn't cover your case.
> Prefer generating patterns from what you already know rather than blocking on a web lookup.